text: Incan is of or pertaining to the Incas, their culture or empire. Incan may also refer to: * of or pertaining to Inca, Spain * Incan berries (also called golden berries), popular with some vegans * Inca people, the people of the Incan Empire * Quechua people, the people of the Incan civilization * Incan language, the language of the Incas ==See also== * Inca (disambiguation) * * * Inkan () seals (stamps) * Quechua (disambiguation)
title: Incan (disambiguation)
